{"arkId":"cl010097621","url":"https:\/\/collections.louvre.fr\/ark:\/53355\/cl010097621","modified ":"2025-08-25","title":"Sablier","titleComplement":"","denominationTitle":[{"type":"Titre","value":"Sablier\r\n"}],"displayDateCreated":"Epoque \/ p\u00e9riode : \u00e9poque moderne = Ancien R\u00e9gime (Occident)\r\n\r\nDate de cr\u00e9ation\/fabrication : 1700 - 1800","currentLocation":"Richelieu, [OArt] Salle 531 - Paul Garnier, Vitrine 1","room":"Salle 531, Aile Aile Richelieu, Niveau 1","isMuseesNationauxRecuperation":false,"dateCreated":[{"startYear":1700,"endYear":1800,"imprecision":"","text":"XVIIIe si\u00e8cle","type":"Date de cr\u00e9ation\/fabrication","doubt":""}],"creator":[{"label":"Anonyme","attributionLevel":"Attribution actuelle","linkType":"","creatorRole":"Fabricant, facteur","authenticationType":"","doubt":"","attributedBy":"","attributedYear":"","wikidata":"Q4233718"}],"objectNumber":[{"value":"OA 10867","type":"Num\u00e9ro principal"}],"collection":"D\u00e9partement des Objets d\u0027art du Moyen Age, de la Renaissance et des temps modernes","printsDrawingsEntity":"","printsDrawingsCollection":"","objectType":"instrument scientifique (mesure, calcul, observation, etc.)","originalObject":"","printState":"","description":"\u0022Le support des fioles est mont\u00e9 par l\u2019interm\u00e9diaire d\u2019une vis \u00e0 pivot sur une branche verticale surmont\u00e9e de chiffres et reposant sur une base octogonale moulur\u00e9e. Ce support, que l\u2019on peut donc retourner \u00e0 l\u2019aide d\u2019une manette, est form\u00e9 de deux platines \u00e0 d\u00e9coupes lob\u00e9es sur lesquelles sont viss\u00e9s huit pilastres \u00e0 corniches ; en bordure, les parapets sont grav\u00e9s de rinceaux et de coquilles. Quatre fioles, pour l\u2019heure, les trois quarts d\u2019heure, les demi-heures et les quart d\u2019heure, sont constitu\u00e9es de deux globules allong\u00e9s dont le joint est couvert d\u2019une toile bleue serr\u00e9e de fils dor\u00e9s. Le sable est de couleur blanche.\u0022 (Fr\u00e9montier-Murphy, 2002)","inscriptions":"Inscription : \r ; chiffres : trois \u0022C\u0022 coiff\u00e9s d\u0027une couronne et encadr\u00e9s de palmes (au sommet du support)\r ; Poin\u00e7on : \r ; un \u0022B\u0022 et un \u0022M\u0022 surmont\u00e9 d\u0027un oiseau [?] (non identifi\u00e9s) (sur le pied)","namesAndTitles":"","onomastics":"","dimension":[{"type":"Hauteur","value":"45,7","displayDimension":"45,7 cm","unit":"cm","anteriorPrecision":"","posteriorPrecision":"","tri":1,"note":""},{"type":"Longueur","value":"19,6","displayDimension":"19,6 cm","unit":"cm","anteriorPrecision":"","posteriorPrecision":"","tri":2,"note":""},{"type":"Largeur","value":"10,7","displayDimension":"10,7 cm","unit":"cm","anteriorPrecision":"","posteriorPrecision":"","tri":3,"note":""}],"shape":"","materialsAndTechniques":"Mat\u00e9riau\/Technique : Argent, verre, sable blanc\r\nMat\u00e9riau : argent\r\nMat\u00e9riau : sable\r\nMat\u00e9riau : verre","placeOfCreation":"Allemagne (Europe)","dateOfDiscovery":"","placeOfDiscovery":"","provenance":"","historicalContext":[],"objectHistory":"Don Marcelle Landau, 1980","jabachInventory":"","napoleonInventory":"","previousOwner":[{"value":"Mme Landau, Marcelle","note":"","role":", Donateur"},{"value":"M. Landau, Nicolas","note":"","role":", Collectionneur"}],"acquisitionDetails":[{"mode":"don manuel","doubt":"","dates":[{"type":"date","value":"1980","startYear":1980,"endYear":1980},{"type":"date de comit\u00e9\/commission","value":"24\/04\/1980","startYear":1980,"endYear":1980}]}],"ownedBy":"Etat","heldBy":"Mus\u00e9e du Louvre, D\u00e9partement des Objets d\u0027art du Moyen Age, de la Renaissance et des temps modernes","longTermLoanTo":"","index":{"Mode d\u0027acquisition":[{"value":"don manuel"}],"period":[{"value":"\u00e9poque moderne = Ancien R\u00e9gime"}],"place":[{"value":"Allemagne"}],"objectType":[{"value":"instrument scientifique (mesure, calcul, observation, etc.)"}]},"bibliography":[{"biblio